{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, NCEL incorporates graph convolutional networks into a deep neural network to utilise structured graph information for collective feature abstraction.",
    "NCEL was compared to 16 other systems focusing on EL [34, 59-61, 68, 73, 76, 93, 117, 122, 135, 141, 177, 181, 193, 199].",
    "The results were compared using the Gerbil 15 benchmark.",
    "The authors also detail the analysis of two corpora, the less complex one (TAC2010) and the most complex one (WIKI and CWeb).Bhatia et al. [22] present a simple, fast, and accurate probabilistic entity-linking algorithm used in the enterprise.",
    "To do this, the authors rely on automatically constructed domainspecific knowledge graphs."
  ]
}